@NODE "MAIN" "SignArch v1.1"
@TOC "Index"
                            @{u}@{b}SignArch v1.1@{uu}@{ub}

       @{"Message digests" LINK "Notes" 18} a list of files, and archives everything
                                  or
                  A Graphical User Interface for LhA
                                  or
                  YAPS (Yet Another @{"PGP" LINK "PGP"} Simplifier)

           Distributed under the GNU General Public License

